						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PhD-Scholarships-in-Plant-Breeding" title="PhD Scholarships in Plant Breeding" alt="link">PhD Scholarships in Plant Breeding</a></h2>

	
					<p>African Centre for Crop Improvement at the University of Kwa-Zulu Natal, South Africa offers this prestigious scholarship to young African Scientists who are keen to make Plant Breeding their career. The scholarship involves two years of academic studies at the University of KwaZulu-Natal and three years of field research in the student home countries, at their home institution.WACCI is currently accepting applications for January 2010 fellowship until September 30, 2009.</p>
							<p><span class="date">4/09/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PhD-Scholarships-in-Plant-Breeding">Read more...</a>
