<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Angus-Sawise-Scholarship" title="Angus Sawise Scholarship " alt="link">Angus Sawise Scholarship </a></h2>

	
					<p>Each year SA WISE awards the Angus Scholarship, to a Sub-Saharan black woman graduate with 70% or above grade average in her subject of study. The scholarship is awarded for 1 year of tertiary study at Honours level (or 4th year level of study) in any field of science and engineering. South African applicants will be given preference. Application deadline: <b>30 November annually</b>.</p>
							<p><span class="date">5/08/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
